long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Subscribe to TECHNOBLADE!!!!! This is a completely free chrome extension, no string attached. This chrome extension causes random Technoblade related phrases to pop up on your screen in different colors. It will also make a little image of Technoblade to float along the border of the screen. If you click the chrome extension multiple times, more phrases show up and more images pop up. If you really are moved to support me though, you can subscribe to youtube channel Lurk:https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCS-x7lD-CSnoc8ejgxrEntQ!
